<%- include("partials/header") %>

<div class="container mt-5" style="max-width: 800px;">
  <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  
  <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">

    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q1">
          1. How do I lodge a complaint on this portal?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="q1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          You can lodge an issue by going to the "Lodge Issues" section on the homepage. Provide details and upload images if necessary.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q2">
          2. Can I track the status of my complaint?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="q2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          Yes, use the "Track Status" feature with your complaint ID or Aadhaar number to view real-time progress.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q3">
          3. Is Aadhaar authentication mandatory?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="q3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          Yes, Aadhaar authentication ensures accountability and prevents misuse of the system.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q4">
          4. How do I contact support if I face issues?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="q4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          You can use the "Contact Us" page to submit queries. Alternatively, reach us on our official social media handles.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header">
        <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#q5">
          5. Are financial reports verified by the government?
        </button>
      </h2>
      <div id="q5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-body">
          Yes, all financial release data is officially verified and directly updated from government sources.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>

<%- include("partials/footer") %>
